# Cloudflare Pages redirect rules.
# No catch-all rule here — this intentionally disables SPA mode so that
# unmatched paths return a real 404 (served via 404.html) instead of 200.

# Canonicalize www → non-www (item 3)
https://www.coastaltravelcompany.com/* https://coastaltravelcompany.com/:splat 301
https://www.preprod.coastaltravelcompany.com/* https://preprod.coastaltravelcompany.com/:splat 301
